  "Say": {
    "_dirName": "Say",
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Well, what do you think? Don't you want to get even more powerful than that? Pass a simple test and I'll do just that for you. Do you want to do it?"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Good decision. You look strong, but I need to see if you really are strong enough to pass the test. It's not a difficult test, so you'll do just fine. Here, take my letter first...make sure you don't lose it!"
        },
        "1": {
          "_dirName": "1",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Please get this letter to the #b#p227##k who's around #b#m10001090##k near #m10001000#. She's taking care of the job of an instructor in place of me. "
        },
        "2": {
          "_dirName": "2",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Give her the letter, and she'll test you in place of me. Best of luck to you."
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirName": "no",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Really? Have to give more thought to it, huh? Take your time, take your time. This is not something you should take lightly...come talk to me once you have made your decision."
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Hmmm... it is definitely the letter from #b#p221##k... so you came all the way here to take the test and make the 2nd job advancement as the bowman?"
